When cloning project for the first time
git submodule init
git submodule update

When pulling from repo and you have no changes to the submodule
git pull
git submodule update

When trying to push changes to the submodule
cd into submodule
git commit and push
cd back
git commit 
git pull and push

If something goes wrong
git pull 
git submodule update
cd into submodule
git pull 
cd back
git commit and push